{"title":"延河飘香","authors":["党永庵"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":1,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"延河飘香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党永庵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣园听歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月夜我访枣园村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣花十里香喷喷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清风迎面过，耳旁飘歌音……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁家女子情意真，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信天游出口句句新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌儿哟，飞过崖畔出枣林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞出枣林荡过岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山峁峁有回音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"招来姑娘、后生一大群……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，原是队里修鱼塘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢时引水争光阴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团支书，竟把歌音作哨音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌音多象报春鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声悦耳情最深——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声里，迎来一个新渔村……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果园写意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月七，八月八，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延河畔，熟透的苹果满枝挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挤飞坡上十里霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们上树摘新果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领头的是那科研组长王桂花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日出忙到月西斜……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果香迎来人一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳下“飞鸽”站树下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是谁？夜大毕业的土专家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一串串车铃藏密语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逗乐了一群女娃娃："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“桂花姐，快把新果摘给他！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“春上他来帮剪枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天又来把农药打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说他，心里想的啥？……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想的啥？桂花不回答，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抿着小嘴羞答答——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香风里，飘下一块花手帕……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}